I'm sorry I said AoL isn't a raiding guild.  What I meant by this is that we don't do raids like Thurg, ToV, or Planes.  Not once have I seen the guild set up to go on a raid with SS or 1fer's to go and do plane flags.  Why? Because we're not necessarily built for that type of thing.  But let's continue<br>
